OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Fthis evening though perhaps the odd
OL,7,Fshower in places, with the chance of a
OL,8,Ffew continuing overnight. Generally
OL,9,Fdry otherwise with clear spells.
OL,10,FTurning chilly with a patchy rural
OL,11,Fgrass frost, though this less
OL,12,Fwidespread than last night.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FDry with spells of cloudy
OL,15,Fweather interspersed with periods of
OL,16,Fsunshine, these most prolonged during
OL,17,Fthe afternoon. Somewhat warmer than on
OL,18,FMonday, though increasingly breezy
OL,19,Fwith an easterly wind developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
