OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FStaying dry through the week with high
OL,7,Fpressure dominating. Often sunny and
OL,8,Fturning warmer by day, but chilly
OL,9,Fnights with rural frosts possible.
OL,10,FBreezy at first but winds becoming
OL,11,Flighter.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
